Tottori University (Private Laboratory) / Eastern buzzard / reverse transcription-polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) / 16 Dec 2020 / Positive
Tottori University (Private Laboratory) / Mandarin Duck / gene sequencing / 9 Dec 2020 / Positive
Tottori University (Private Laboratory) / Mandarin Duck / reverse transcription-polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) / 9 Dec 2020 / Positive
Tottori University (Private Laboratory) / Peregrin falcon / gene sequencing / 9 Dec 2020 / Positive
Tottori University (Private Laboratory) / Peregrin falcon / reverse transcription-polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) / 9 Dec 2020 / Positive

Future reporting
The event is continuing. Weekly follow-up reports will be submitted.

[The location of the outbreak can be seen on the interactive map included in the OIE report at the source URL above.]

